Despite concerns from various members of the party, we have authorized the transfer of resources. Utilizing the necessary logistics, we managed go smuggle essentials & weapons to dissidents in Spain. Though the governments in London and Paris cannot fully openly proof our interference in "Spanish internal affairs," they suspect we are providing aid. Despite this we proven the German SPD still aids those in the struggle against the bourgeoisie.   

@abstain
